      "datePublished": "2024-09-15",
      "reviewBody": "Absolutely incredible bachelor party experience on the ATX Disco Cruise! The professional DJ kept the energy high all day, and our photographer captured amazing moments. The groom cruised free with our group of 18, making it super affordable. Best bachelor party decision we made in Austin!"
    },
