      "datePublished": "2024-08-22",
      "reviewBody": "Our bachelorette party on Lake Travis was unforgettable! The Disco Queen package was perfect - the bride cruised free, we had our own cooler setup, and the giant unicorn float made for epic photos. The atmosphere with other bachelorette groups was so fun. Highly recommend!"
