      "datePublished": "2024-07-10",
      "reviewBody": "We booked a private boat for our corporate team building event and it exceeded all expectations. The 25-person boat was perfect for our team, captain was professional, and Premier Party Cruises coordinated everything seamlessly including catering. Our employees are still talking about it!"
    },
