      "datePublished": "2024-06-28",
      "reviewBody": "Best bachelorette party boat in Austin, hands down! The Super Sparkle Platinum package was worth every penny - personal unicorn float for the bride, mimosa setup, professional photos, and VIP treatment. The 4-hour cruise flew by. Brian and his team made everything perfect!"
    },
