      "datePublished": "2024-05-18",
      "reviewBody": "Threw my buddy's bachelor party on the Disco Cruise and it was legendary! Way better value than renting a private boat. The DJ was amazing, we got hundreds of professional photos, and the energy with other bachelor groups was electric. The groom cruised free too. Can't beat it!"
    },
