      "datePublished": "2024-04-12",
      "reviewBody": "Premier Party Cruises made our milestone birthday celebration unforgettable! We rented the 50-person Clever Girl boat and it was spectacular. The disco balls, giant Texas flag, and professional crew created an incredible party atmosphere. Brian was so helpful with planning every detail!"
